Package com.db4o.qlin

Interface Summary
QLin<T> a node in a QLin ("Coolin") query.
QLinable support for the new experimental QLin ("Coolin") query interface.
 

Class Summary
Prototypes creates prototype objects for classes.
QLinSupport static import support class for QLin queries.
 

Exception Summary
PrototypesException exception for the the Prototypes world.
QLinException exceptions to signal improper use of the QLin query interface.
